          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="labelFormulaText">
            <property name="sizePolicy">
             <sizepolicy hsizetype="Preferred" vsizetype="Fixed">
              <horstretch>0</horstretch>
              <verstretch>0</verstretch>
             </sizepolicy>
            </property>
            <property name="styleSheet">
             <string notr="true">QLabel {
    color: rgb(80, 80, 80);                  /* soft dark gray */
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Roboto&quot;, sans-serif;
}</string>
            </property>
            <property name="text">
             <string>CC LOW FREQUENCY RESPONSE

RB is entered directly.

REL = RE || RL
RSB = RS || RB
RXX = rπ + (β + 1)REL

R11 = RS + (RB || RXX)
f1 = 1 / (2π R11 C1)

R22 = RL + { RE || [(rπ + RSB)/(β + 1)] }
f2 = 1 / (2π R22 C2)

max(f1, f2) ≤ fL ≤ f1 + f2
Conservative: fL = max(f1, f2)</string>
            </property>
            <property name="wordWrap">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
           </widget>
